episodes.title: Exploring Japan’s Suicide Forest: The Hidden Village of the Most Dangerous Cult
episodes.description:
Deep inside Japan’s infamous Aokigahara, also known as the Suicide Forest, lies a mysterious hidden village connected to Japan’s darkest past. In this video, I explore the eerie forests at the base of Mount Fuji, uncovering traces of the Aum Shinrikyo cult and the secrets they left behind. Join me as we walk through one of the most chilling places in Japan, where beauty and darkness coexist.
